        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Hydrogen for Ports Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill supports infrastructure for hydrogen-derived fuels, including ammonia, at ports and in the shipping industry. For example, the bill directs the Department of Energy to establish a program that awards grants to states, local governments, Indian tribes, and other eligible entities for infrastructure that supports hydrogen-derived fuels, including ammonia, at ports and in the shipping industry.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
